'''2016年土耳其政變'''（[[土耳其語|土耳其語]]：{{lang|tr|2016 Türkiye askerî darbe girişimi}}），指[[土耳其|土耳其]]軍方内部派系在2016年7月15日企圖进行[[政變|政變]]推翻总统[[雷傑普·塔伊普·埃爾多安|雷傑普·塔伊普·埃爾多安]]<ref name="Turkish Military Says It Has Seized Control From Ankara Government " /><ref name=haber7 />，冀希望达到中断土耳其[[伊斯兰化|伊斯兰化]]的目的，但最后以失败告终<ref name="Turkish Military Says It Has Seized Control From Ankara Government ">{{cite web | url=http://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/1.731225 | title=Turkish Military Says It Has Seized Control From Ankara Government | accessdate=2016-07-15 | archive-date=2016-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715222337/http://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/1.731225 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="haber7">{{cite news|url=http://www.haber7.com/ic-politika/haber/2046645-1-ordu-komutanindan-aciklama|title=1. Ordu Komutanı'ndan açıklama!|work=haber7.com|language=tr|trans-title=Explanation from the commander of the 1st Army !|date=2016-07-16|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401181206/http://www.haber7.com/ic-politika/haber/2046645-1-ordu-komutanindan-aciklama|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这场未遂政变造成至少265人死亡和数千名群众受伤，當晚有報導稱位於[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]的[[土耳其国会|土耳其国会]]大厦以及{{le|土耳其总统府|Presidential Complex|土耳其总统府}}皆遭到轰炸<ref name=FOXimage /><ref name=CelikParliament /><ref name="rt_casaulties">{{cite web|title=Shootout with mass casualties reported in central Ankara, over 150 injured in Istanbul|url=https://www.rt.com/news/351472-turkish-coup-shooting-casualties/|website=rt.com|publisher=Russia Today|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225063753/https://www.rt.com/news/351472-turkish-coup-shooting-casualties/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]和[[伊斯坦堡|伊斯坦布尔]]的机场内，也能听到枪击声<ref name="APLiveBlog" />。

這次政變始於7月15日晚上有軍人奉命封鎖[[博斯普魯斯海峽大橋|博斯普魯斯海峽大橋]]其中一條行車線<ref name="thestandnews-2020-01-13">{{cite news |title=土耳其 — 來自神的禮物 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6-%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%AE%E7%89%A9/ |accessdate=2020-01-16 |work=立場新聞 |date=2020-01-13 |archive-date=2020-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114170706/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6-%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%AE%E7%89%A9/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而海軍艦艇收到命令要全部出海候命，但海軍司令卻在期間失聯，也沒有任何政府領導層被叛軍拘禁，埃爾多安在半夜的電視直播聲稱有人發動政變及鼓勵民眾上街對付謀反的士兵，隨後便有配備武器的民眾追打士兵，警察卻視而不見，海軍艦艇奉命返回基地後便有多名指揮官遭到埃爾多安政府拘捕，政府在政變發生當晚已拘捕數千人，政變過程疑點重重<ref name="chinatimes-2016-07-18">{{cite news |title=「這場暴亂是真主送的大禮」 土國政變 疑總統自導自演 |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160718000324-260102?chdtv |accessdate=2020-01-16 |work=中時電子報 |date=2016-07-18 |archive-date=2021-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602075203/https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160718000324-260102?chdtv |dead-url=no }}</ref>，當晚報稱有叛軍包圍政府大樓及空襲總統府等，事後證實根本從未發生，埃爾多安政府在之後的[[2016年土耳其整肅|大整肅]]，有數以萬計的軍人及公務員被拘留及開除，大量學校、新聞媒體與政治組織被解散及關閉，有紀錄片直指這場「政變」是總統埃爾多安為獨攬大權及剷除異己而自編自導自演<ref name="chinatimes-2016-07-18"/><ref name="rthk-31-613868">{{Cite web |url=https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/613868 |title=香港電台 31 看世界  土耳其 - 來自神的禮物 |accessdate=2020-01-15 |archive-date=2020-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115135945/https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/613868 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，埃爾多安政府與[[美國|美國]]及[[歐盟|歐盟]]的關係亦自此惡化<ref name="udn-2019-05-29">{{cite news |title=土耳其人權經濟惡化 歐盟執委會：入盟希望渺茫 |url=https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3842188 |accessdate=2020-01-16 |work=聯合報 |date=2019-05-29 |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116101720/https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3842188 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
{{Further|土耳其历史|土耳其政变问题}}
自[[凯末尔|凯末尔]]上台后，他试图把土耳其改造成世俗化的民族国家，令宗教逐步脱离民众的正常生活。歷史上，土耳其軍方也被認為是[[穆斯塔法·凯末尔·阿塔图尔克|凱末爾]]建立的世俗化土耳其共和國的捍衛者<ref name="ArangoNYT" />，现行土耳其宪法赋予了土耳其军队维护土耳其世俗化社会不被破坏的职责。土耳其自1946年施行多黨民主後，在土耳其社会走向伊斯兰化的关键时刻[[土耳其军事|土耳其军隊]]主導了三次政變，分別於[[1960年土耳其政變|1960年]]、{{link-en|1971年土耳其政變|1971 Turkish military memorandum|1971年}}、{{link-en|1980年土耳其政變|1980 Turkish coup d'état|1980年}}以及1997年的{{link-en|1997年土耳其政變|1997 Turkish military memorandum|軍事干預}}<ref name="ArangoNYT">{{cite news |author1=[[Tim_Arango|Tim Arango]] |author2=[[Ceylan_Yeğinsu|Ceylan Yeğinsu]] |date=2016-07-15 |title=President of Turkey Urges Resistance as Military Attempts Coup |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/world/europe/military-attempts-coup-in-turkey-prime-minister-says.html |accessdate=2016-07-15 |archive-date=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715205242/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/world/europe/military-attempts-coup-in-turkey-prime-minister-says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

土耳其總統[[埃爾多安|埃爾多安]]所在的[[正义与发展党_(土耳其)|正義與發展黨]]被認為是土耳其成为共和国以来的第五代亲伊斯兰政党。[[正义与发展党_(土耳其)|正义与发展党]]认为，[[凯末尔主义|凯末尔主义]]导致伊斯兰信仰在土国内的瓦解是当今土耳其内政外交问题的根源，因此不断鼓动宗教情绪、恢复伊斯兰信仰。[[正义与发展党_(土耳其)|正義與發展黨]]的主张受到从凯末尔时代以来就被压制多年的宗教保守派人士的支持<ref>[https://www.jiemian.com/article/757912.html 为什么土耳其人喜欢“独裁者”埃尔多安？] {{Wayback|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/757912.html |date=20180724062825 }}.界面.</ref><ref>[http://view.163.com/16/0717/01/BS4VMUAU00015AAR.html 土耳其政变，世俗主义对伊斯兰化的一次未遂反击] {{Wayback|url=http://view.163.com/16/0717/01/BS4VMUAU00015AAR.html |date=20180724062642 }}.网易新闻.</ref>。

== 政变经过 ==
===政变方试图掌权===
2016年7月15日[[欧洲东部夏令时间|当地时间]]（UTC+3）接近23:00，民眾目睹[[軍機|軍機]]出现在[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]上空，[[穆罕默德二世大桥|穆罕默德二世大桥]]与[[博斯普鲁斯大桥|博斯普鲁斯大桥]]自[[安纳托利亚|安纳托利亚]]至[[欧洲|欧洲]]的方向封闭<ref name="APLiveBlog" /><ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/turkey-low-flying-jets-and-gunfire-heard-in-ankara1/|title=Turkey coup: military attempt to seize power from Erdoğan as low-flying jets and gunfire heard in Ankara and bridges across Bosphorus in Istanbul closed|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716054020/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/turkey-low-flying-jets-and-gunfire-heard-in-ankara1/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/turkish-prime-minister-reports-coup-attempt-1468613584|title=Turkish Prime Minister Reports Coup Attempt|date=2016-07-15|work=WSJ|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715222442/http://www.wsj.com/articles/turkish-prime-minister-reports-coup-attempt-1468613584|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

時任[[土耳其总理|土耳其总理]][[比纳利·耶伊尔德勒姆|比纳利·耶伊尔德勒姆]]称军队“受到了外界的命令”，一部分军人试图夺取[[权力|权力]]，并称这是“非法的行动”<ref name="Turkish Military Says It Has Seized Control From Ankara Government "/>。他进一步表示，这些参与者“将会付出极大的代价”<ref name="buzzfeed">{{cite web |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/jimdalrympleii/violence-erupts-in-turkish-capital |title=Turkey's Prime Minister Says Attempted Military Coup Underway – BuzzFeed News |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716104936/https://www.buzzfeed.com/jimdalrympleii/violence-erupts-in-turkish-capital |dead-url=no }}</ref>。当地媒体也报道[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]的[[阿塔图尔克国际机场|阿塔图尔克国际机场]]出现了坦克<ref name="BBC2">{{cite news |title=Turkey army group announces takeover on TV |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36809083 |newspaper=BBC News |access-date=2016-07-16 |archive-date=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715220712/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36809083 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，土耳其境内用户无法登陆[[Twitter|Twitter]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]和[[YouTube|YouTube]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://qz.com/733762/turkish-military-seizes-state-power-according-to-media-reports-jets-flyover-ankara-istanbuls-bridges-closed/ |title=Turkish military seizes power according to media reports; jets flyover Ankara, Istanbul’s bridges closed — Quartz |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716122445/http://qz.com/733762/turkish-military-seizes-state-power-according-to-media-reports-jets-flyover-ankara-istanbuls-bridges-closed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Mirror">{{cite web |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/turkey-coup-live-updates-explosion-8431256#rlabs=1%20rt$category%20p$4 |title=Turkey 'coup': Live updates as explosion and gunfire reported in capital Ankara – Mirror Online |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402022426/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/turkey-coup-live-updates-explosion-8431256#rlabs=1%20rt$category%20p$4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，Twitter随后表示，他们并不认为有原因使得他们被封锁<ref>{{cite tweet |author=Twitter's global public policy team |user=policy |number=754072148289789952 |date=2016-07-15 |script-title=en:We have no reason to think we’ve been fully blocked in #Turkey, but we suspect there is an intentional slowing of our traffic in country. }}</ref>。军队总部内，{{le|土耳其总参谋长|Chief of the Turkish General Staff|土耳其参谋总长}}[[胡卢西·阿卡爾|胡卢西·阿卡爾]]遭到俘虏<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/turkey-low-flying-jets-and-gunfire-heard-in-ankara1/|title=Live: Turkey coup|publisher=''Daily Telegraph''|accessdate=2016-07-15|date=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716054020/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/turkey-low-flying-jets-and-gunfire-heard-in-ankara1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，军队也进入[[正义与发展党_(土耳其)|正义与发展党]]在伊斯坦布尔的办事处，要求人员离开<ref>{{cite tweet |author=Sky News Newsdesk |user=SkyNewsBreak |number=754060027300904962 |date=2016-07-15 |title=Update – Turkish media reports soldiers have entered #Turkey's ruling party's #Istanbul offices and have asked people to leave }}</ref>。

报导指出，[[土耳其总统|土耳其总统]][[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安]]当时正在土耳其西南的[[马尔马里斯港|马尔马里斯港]][[度假|度假]]<ref name="auto" />，他已经乘坐私人飞机飞离国内<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/breaking-gunfire-reported-ankara-military-8431619|title=Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdoğan 'flees country in private jet' after military launches coup|last=Rkaina|first=Sam|date=2016-07-15|newspaper=Daily Mirror|access-date=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715221419/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/breaking-gunfire-reported-ankara-military-8431619|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://t24.com.tr/haber/erdogandan-ilk-aciklama-bir-azinligin-kalkinma-hareketidir,350163|title=Erdoğan'dan ilk açıklama: Milletimizi meydanlara davet ediyorum; en ağır bedeli ödeyecekler!|work=t24.com.tr|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6j2vTCzEQ?url=http://t24.com.tr/haber/erdogandan-ilk-aciklama-bir-azinligin-kalkinma-hareketidir,350163|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

大约在23:00与00:00间，直升机攻击了位于{{link-en|格爾巴舍|Gölbaşı, Ankara}}（安卡拉郊外）的特种部队总部和空军总部，造成42人死亡和43人受伤。{{le|Türksat 卫星通信与有线电视运营公司|Türksat_(company)}}在Gölbaşı的总部也遭到攻击，两名安保人员被杀害<ref>{{cite web|title=Gölbaşı'ndaki patlamada 42 şehit, 43 yaralı var|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/ankara-haberleri/golbasi-ndaki-patlamada-42-sehit-43-yarali-var_310100/|publisher=Hürriyet|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725173222/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/ankara-haberleri/golbasi-ndaki-patlamada-42-sehit-43-yarali-var_310100|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="latimes.com">{{cite web|title=Turkey coup attempt: President Erdogan says the government is in control|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/la-fg-turkey-unrest-helicopted-fire-kills-17-police-1468624244-htmlstory.html|website=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2016-07-16|date=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716055255/http://www.latimes.com/world/la-fg-turkey-unrest-helicopted-fire-kills-17-police-1468624244-htmlstory.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

23:50左右，政变士兵占领了位于[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]中央的[[塔克西姆广场|塔克西姆广场]]<ref name="diken">{{cite web|title=Darbe girişimi | 161 kişi hayatını kaybetti, 1440 kişi yaralandı|url=http://www.diken.com.tr/darbe-girisimi-90-kisi-hayatini-kaybetti-darbeye-tesebbus-eden-104-kisi-olduruldu/|publisher=Diken|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912090122/http://www.diken.com.tr/gozaltindaki-asker-sayisi-6-bin-746-1258i-tutuklu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

7月16日凌晨0:02，[[路透社|路透社]]报导，政变军队已进入土耳其的国家媒体[[土耳其广播电视公司|土耳其广播电视公司]]的建筑内<ref name="guardian" />。政变期间，军队强迫主播{{le|提简·卡拉斯|Tijen Karaş}}宣读声明，称“土耳其的民主与世俗原则已被现在的政府所破坏”，国家“已被{{le|土耳其和平委员会|Turkish Peace Council|土耳其和平委员会}}控制”，该组织将会确保首都内人民的安全<ref name="Mirror" /><ref name="karas">{{cite web|url=http://onedio.com/haber/tijen-karas-bildiriyi-silah-zoru-altinda-okudum-hayatimin-en-zor-yayiniydi--721477|title=Tijen Karaş: "Bildiriyi Silah Zoru Altında Okudum, Hayatımın En Zor Yayınıydı"|publisher=''Onedio''|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401192225/https://onedio.com/haber/tijen-karas-bildiriyi-silah-zoru-altinda-okudum-hayatimin-en-zor-yayiniydi--721477|dead-url=no}}</ref>，声明一部分还提到“土耳其军队已经接管了国家，恢复了被破坏的宪法秩序、人权、自由和安全......所有的国际协议仍然有效，我们希望仍然与其他国家保持良好关系”<ref name="guardian">{{cite news |last1=Levin |first1=Sam |last2=Rawlinson |first2=Kevin |date=2016-07-16 |title=Turkey military coup: tanks open fire near parliament building – live updates |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jul/15/turkey-coup-attempt-military-gunfire-ankara |newspaper=The Guardian |access-date=2016-07-16 |archive-date=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715234833/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jul/15/turkey-coup-attempt-military-gunfire-ankara |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="JPost">{{cite web |title=Turkish military has said in a statement that the military has taken over |website=The Jerusalem Post |date=2016-07-15 |url=http://www.jpost.com/International/Turkish-Prime-Minister-says-military-coup-attempt-underway-460533 |accessdate=2016-07-15 |archive-date=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715222451/http://www.jpost.com/International/Turkish-Prime-Minister-says-military-coup-attempt-underway-460533 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，政变的策划者称“他们已经维护了民主秩序，法律必须保持优先”，该声明还下达了[[戒严令|戒严令]]，称将会尽快制定新的[[宪法|宪法]]<ref name="BBC">{{cite news |title=Turkey sees army coup attempt |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/live/world-europe-36811357 |newspaper=BBC News |access-date=2016-07-16 |archive-date=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715232428/http://www.bbc.com/news/live/world-europe-36811357 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnbc.com/2016/07/15/gunfire-heard-jets-seen-flying-in-turkish-capital-of-ankara.html|title=Attempted military coup unfolding in Turkey|last=Wang|first=Everett Rosenfeld, Ted Kemp, Christine|date=2016-07-16|website=CNBC|access-date=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715215739/http://www.cnbc.com/2016/07/15/gunfire-heard-jets-seen-flying-in-turkish-capital-of-ankara.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，随后土耳其广播电视公司停播节目<ref name="guardian" />。

