土耳其总统办公室表示，[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|埃尔多安]]总统在土耳其境外度假且十分安全，并谴责政变是对民主的破坏<ref name="BBC2" /><ref name=guardian />。总统的消息人士称埃尔多安和他的政府仍然掌权<ref name="BBC" />。埃尔多安的首条对外消息于00:23传出<ref name="hurmarmaris">{{cite web|title=Erdoğan Marmaris'ten ayrıldı, kaldığı otel bombalandı|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/mugla-haberleri/erdogan-marmaris-ten-ayrildi-kaldigi-otel-bomb_310005/|publisher=Hürriyet|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717160600/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/mugla-haberleri/erdogan-marmaris-ten-ayrildi-kaldigi-otel-bomb_310005/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凌晨1:00，埃尔多安通过[[FaceTime|FaceTime]]接受来自[[CNN土耳其|CNN土耳其]]的采访，希望他的支持者们走上街头，无视军队强迫下达的宵禁指令，称“没有什么力量高过人民，让在广场和机场里做他们想做的事吧”<ref name="ArangoNYT"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jul/15/turkey-coup-attempt-military-gunfire-ankara?page=with:block-57895c1ae4b033b610b6e3fc#block-57895c1ae4b033b610b6e3fc|title=Turkey coup attempt: Erdoğan calls military uprising 'treason' – live updates|last=Rawlinson|first=Kevin|last2=Phipps|first2=Claire|date=2016-07-16|website=the Guardian|publisher=|access-date=2016-07-16|last3=Levin|first3=Sam|last4=Kingsley|first4=Patrick|last5=Beaumont|first5=Peter|last6=Lewis|first6=Paul|last7=Abdul-Ahad|first7=Ghaith|last8=Wong|first8=Julia Carrie|last9=Yuhas|first9=Alan|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716225830/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jul/15/turkey-coup-attempt-military-gunfire-ankara?page=with:block-57895c1ae4b033b610b6e3fc#block-57895c1ae4b033b610b6e3fc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。副總理{{le|努曼·庫爾圖爾穆什|Numan Kurtulmuş}}出现在电视直播，指出[[正义与发展党_(土耳其)|正义与发展党]]仍然掌控着政府<ref name="BBC" />。即使政变方实行宵禁，正义与发展党籍的[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]市长{{le|梅利赫·戈克切克|Melih Gökçek}}鼓励人们上街抗争<ref name="Mirror" />。埃尔多安的飞机11:47于{{le|达拉曼机场|Dalaman_Airport}}起飞，但由于需要确保伊斯坦布尔机场的安全，飞机只能在[[比加_(恰納卡萊省)|比加]]等候，直到2:50才得以降落<ref>{{cite web|title=Erdoğan'ın uçağı Atatürk Havalimanı'na indi|url=http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2016/gundem/erdoganin-ucagi-havada-bekliyor-1316379/|publisher=Sözcü|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717154412/http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2016/gundem/erdoganin-ucagi-havada-bekliyor-1316379/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

位于[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]的{{le|第一军团 (土耳其)|First Army (Turkey)|土耳其第一军团}}司令部声称，土耳其军队并不支持政变，政变的发起者是军队内的一小部分派系，政变军队正在遭受控制<ref name="haber7"/>。所有伊斯坦布尔机场的航班被取消<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-security-airport-flights-idUSKCN0ZV2K1?mod=related&channelName=worldNews|title=All flights from Istanbul's Ataturk airport canceled: Reuters witness|agency=Reuters|work=|accessdate=|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817155323/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-security-airport-flights-idUSKCN0ZV2K1?mod=related&channelName=worldNews|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据BBC报导，土耳其广播电视公司总部传出爆炸声，安卡拉也传出了枪声<ref name="BBC" />。不久后，平民和警察冲入土耳其广播电视公司，据称在内的4名士兵被制服，电视台恢复了播出，之前被强迫宣布声明的{{le|提簡·卡拉斯|Tijen Karaş}}在节目中表示她被挟持，且是在被枪口对着的情况下宣读声明<ref>{{cite web|title=Kalkışma girişimindeki askerler TRT'de korsan bildiri okuttu|url=http://www.haberturk.com/gundem/haber/1267349-kalkisma-girisimindeki-askerler-trtde-korsan-bildiri-okuttu|publisher=Habertürk|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716134710/http://www.haberturk.com/gundem/haber/1267349-kalkisma-girisimindeki-askerler-trtde-korsan-bildiri-okuttu|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

凌晨1:00，有报道指出政变方已经将力量从机场转移，人群正在进入机场，但在1:13，机场又传出坦克开火的声音<ref name="diken" />。

坦克于[[土耳其大国民议会|土耳其议会大厦]]附近开火<ref name="guardian" />，同时议会大厦也遭到了来自空中的攻击<ref name=FOXimage /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/story/live-turkish-army-says-taken-power-over-country-10503062 |title=LIVE: Gunfire And injuries On Istanbul Bridge |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716141921/http://news.sky.com/story/live-turkish-army-says-taken-power-over-country-10503062 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据报导，位于[[博斯普魯斯大橋|博斯普魯斯大橋]]上跟随政变军队的抗议者遭到伤害<ref name=CelikParliament /><ref name="BBC" />。

一架土耳其军方的[[F-16|F-16]]击落了政变军队的直升机<ref name="BBC" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/07/15/world/live-blog-turkey/index.html|title=Turkey coup: Live updates – CNN.com|format=|work=|accessdate=|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716122953/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/07/15/world/live-blog-turkey/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有报道声称，安卡拉上空出现了政府军队的飞机，以消灭政变军队的直升机<ref name="BBC" />。

凌晨3:08，一架军用直升机对着议会大厦开火<ref name="diken" />，3:10，土耳其军队通过其网站，声称已经控制全国<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tsk.tr/BasinFaaliyetleri/BA_188|title=Türk Silahlı Kuvvetleri Genelkurmay Başkanlığı|publisher=|access-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716003423/http://www.tsk.tr/BasinFaaliyetleri/BA_188|archive-date=2016-07-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。3:12，[[比纳利·耶伊尔德勒姆|比纳利·耶伊尔德勒姆]]表示局势已经得到控制，军队会在安卡拉上空设立禁飞区，任何军用飞机飞入都将被击落<ref name="diken" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Başbakan Yıldırım: Ankara semalarında uçuş yapan her türlü uçak füzeyle düşürülecektir!|url=http://haber.star.com.tr/guncel/binali-yildirim--ankara-semalarinda-ucus-yapan-her-turlu-ucak-fuzeyle-dusurulecektir/haber-1125727|publisher=Star|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717140741/http://haber.star.com.tr/guncel/binali-yildirim--ankara-semalarinda-ucus-yapan-her-turlu-ucak-fuzeyle-dusurulecektir/haber-1125727|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在3:23和3:33，报导称土耳其议会大厦再次爆炸<ref name="explosion">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/turkey-coup-erdogan/bomb-at-parliament-leaves-12-dead/|title=Bomb at Parliament Kills 12, CNN Turk Reports|author=|work=The New York Times|date=2016-07-15|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716063738/http://www.nytimes.com/live/turkey-coup-erdogan/bomb-at-parliament-leaves-12-dead/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，当时一架政变军队的直升机被目击到在旁，CNN土耳其报导了新闻，称造成12人死亡，2人严重受伤。CNN报导该新闻后30分钟后，政变士兵进入CNN 土耳其的总部，强迫其停止播出节目<ref name="guardian" /><ref name="BBC" /><ref name="explosion" />。1小时后，CNN又恢复了广播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.teletrader.com/cnn-turk-resumes-program/news/details/35222938?ts=1468636800842|title=CNN Turk resumes program|last=|first=|date=2016-07-15|work=Teletrader|access-date=2016-07-15|via=|archive-date=2016-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814200916/http://www.teletrader.com/cnn-turk-resumes-program/news/details/35222938?ts=1468636800842|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久，土耳其议会議長{{le|伊斯梅爾·卡赫拉曼|İsmail Kahraman}}表示炸弹在议会内公共关系楼群的一个角落爆炸，无人伤亡，而一些人在与警察的冲突中受伤<ref name="AP" />。

凌晨4:00，在埃尔多安离开他的酒店一个半小时后，2-3架直升机袭击了埃尔多安住过的酒店。同时根据目击者描述，10-15名携带武装的人士登陆，开始进行的攻击。随后的冲突造成2名警察死亡，8名警察受伤<ref name="hurmarmaris"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Marmaris'te Erdoğan'ın oteli vuruldu!|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/marmaris-te-helikopterden-ates-gundem-2278703/|publisher=Milliyet|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160716162046/http://www.milliyet.com.tr/marmaris-te-helikopterden-ates-gundem-2278703/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Marmaris'te Cumhurbaşkanı'nın Kaldığı Oteldeki Çatışmalar Sabaha Kadar Sürdü|url=http://www.haberler.com/marmaris-te-cumhurbaskani-nin-kaldigi-oteldeki-8613959-haberi/|publisher=Haberler|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719020847/http://www.haberler.com/marmaris-te-cumhurbaskani-nin-kaldigi-oteldeki-8613959-haberi|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

据土耳其通讯社Doğan News Agency报导，在[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]内，政变军队向试图穿越[[博斯普魯斯大橋|博斯普魯斯大橋]]抗议的人群开火，并造成部分人群受伤<ref name="APLiveBlog">{{cite news|authors=Suzan Fraser & Dominique Soguel|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/c33756424b73481db0655f4c3aed480f/turkish-military-attempted-coup-prime-minister-says|title=Turkish officials say coup attempt appears to have failed|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2018-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913120239/http://berkmancenter_webfeeds:@Pwf$97257@bigstory.ap.org/article/c33756424b73481db0655f4c3aed480f/turkish-military-attempted-coup-prime-minister-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>，政府的支持者对参与政变的士兵进行了斩首<ref>{{cite news|title=Turkish soldier 'beheaded by pro-government mob on Istanbul's Bosphorus Bridge' after failed coup attempt|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/turkish-soldier-beheaded-pro-government-8433319|agency=Mirror|date=2016-07-16|accessdate=2016-07-17|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716181702/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/turkish-soldier-beheaded-pro-government-8433319|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

17名土耳其警察在位于安卡拉外的土耳其特种部队总部外遭到直升机攻击后丧生<ref name="latimes.com"/>。

=== 政变的失败 ===
埃尔多安于凌晨4:00左右到达伊斯坦布尔机场，他在机场进行了讲演，由電視播送，外则有数千名的支持者。6:30时，他再次進行了電視演說，提到他的支持者们，还说道“在土耳其，军队不會统治或者领导国家，他们也不能这么做”，他指责“那些在[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]的人”（暗指[[法图拉·葛兰|法图拉·葛兰]]以及[[居伦运动|居伦运动]]）企图发动政变。他表示，他将会“清理”军队，也称“这次政变是来自[[真主|真主]]的礼物”，為「清理」軍隊提供了理由。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/erdogan-launches-crackdown-after-failed-coup-in-turkey/3421297.html |title=Erdogan Launches Crackdown After Failed Coup in Turkey |publisher=美國之音 |date=2016-07-16 |accessdate=2016-07-17 |archive-date=2016-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717150152/http://www.voanews.com/content/erdogan-launches-crackdown-after-failed-coup-in-turkey/3421297.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[欧洲东部时间|欧洲东部时间]]（UTC+2）7月16日11:42，一架土耳其的[[黑鹰直升机|黑鹰直升机]]向[[希腊|希腊]]发出求救信号，并在8分钟后（11:50）在两架希腊[[F-16戰隼戰鬥機|F-16]]护航下降落在[[亞歷山德魯波利斯|亞歷山德魯波利斯]]机场，直升机降落后7名军事人员和1位平民由于非法入境遭到逮捕，随后他们申请[[政治庇護|政治庇护]]，直升机由希腊控制。土耳其外交部长[[梅夫吕特·恰武什奥卢|梅夫吕特·恰武什奥卢]]表示土耳其希望引渡逃到希腊的人员并将直升机归还给土耳其<ref name="guardian" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkey-demands-return-of-eight-plotter-soldiers-who-landed-on-greece.aspx?pageID=238&nID=101689&NewsCatID=510|title=Turkey demands return of eight plotter soldiers who landed on Greece|publisher=hurriyetdailynews|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716214107/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/turkey-demands-return-of-eight-plotter-soldiers-who-landed-on-greece.aspx?pageID=238&nID=101689&NewsCatID=510|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailysabah.com/politics/2016/07/16/7-pro-coup-soldiers-1-civilian-seeking-asylum-arrested-in-greece|title=7 pro-coup soldiers, 1 civilian seeking asylum arrested in Greece|publisher=dailysabah|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717145722/http://www.dailysabah.com/politics/2016/07/16/7-pro-coup-soldiers-1-civilian-seeking-asylum-arrested-in-greece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

