== 評論 ==
这场政变在国际和国内都遭到了批评声，土耳其主要的反对党发表了谴责<ref name=mhp_oppose>[http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/opposition-parties-reject-the-military-coup-attempt.aspx?pageID=238&nID=101670&NewsCatID=341 Opposition parties reject the military coup attempt] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/opposition-parties-reject-the-military-coup-attempt.aspx?pageID=238&nID=101670&NewsCatID=341 |date=20160716124930 }}, ''{{tsl|en|Hürriyet Daily News||Hürriyet Daily News}}'' (15 July 2016).</ref><ref name=hdp_oppose>{{cite tweet |author=Mutlu Civiroglu |user=mutludc |number=754084935456198656 |date=2016-07-15 |title=HDP Cochairs: "...HDP is under all circumstances and as a matter of principle against all kinds of coup..." }}</ref>，[[欧盟|欧盟]]、[[北约|北约]]和[[美国|美国]]则认为应当尊重土耳其的民选政府。

有意見認為埃爾多安可能會仿效1933年[[魏瑪共和國|德國]]總理[[阿道夫·希特勒|阿道夫·希特勒]]利用[[国会纵火案|国会纵火案]]作藉口，剝奪[[公民自由|公民自由]]和大舉拘捕反對者。超過2,700名土耳其法官在政變後迅即被解除職務一事，加深了一些人的憂慮。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/turkey-coup-conspiracy-theory-erdogan-military-gift-from-god-soldiers-istanbul-a7140516.html |title=Turkey coup: Conspiracy theorists claim attempt was faked by Erdogan |publisher=The Independent |date=2016-07-16 |accessdate=2016-07-16 |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716132404/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/turkey-coup-conspiracy-theory-erdogan-military-gift-from-god-soldiers-istanbul-a7140516.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>被埃爾多安指摘是政變幕後黑手的[[法图拉·葛兰|法图拉·葛兰]]否認指控。葛蘭說本次政變有可能是政府策劃。葛蘭的一名顧問說7月15日的政變策劃不周，「實行得很差勁，所有事看來都是對埃爾多安有利」，留下許多大疑問。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/16/fethullah-gulen-turkey-coup-erdogan |title=Fethullah Gülen: Turkey coup may have been 'staged' by Erdoğan regime |publisher=The Guardian |date=2016-07-16 |accessdate=2016-07-17 |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716221649/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/16/fethullah-gulen-turkey-coup-erdogan |dead-url=no }}</ref>

也有評論認為政變「拙不拙劣」有點以成敗論的色彩，要是成功不管中間再多差錯事後都會被說成計畫詳密，反之亦然。要是政府不透過手機直撥叫出群眾，且群眾願意回應，其實事態發展未可知。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-security-plot-insight-idUKKCN0ZX0Q9 |title=At height of Turkish coup bid, rebel jets had Erdogan's plane in their sights |accessdate=2016-07-23 |archive-date=2016-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722135502/http://uk.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-security-plot-insight-idUKKCN0ZX0Q9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 影響 ==
政變發生後，土耳其政府认为居住在美国的土耳其宗教人士[[法图拉·居连|法图拉·居连]]是政变主谋，一再要求美国将居伦引渡回土耳其，并将他领导的[[居伦运动|居伦运动]]列为恐怖组织，但美国方面始终以“证据不足”为由，拒绝这一诉求<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.cctv.com/2018/01/12/ARTIljO2qF9aBsuicobXW9pM180112.shtml |title=美国拒绝引渡居伦 土耳其 埃尔多安：土将不再向美引渡嫌疑人 |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216113200/http://news.cctv.com/2018/01/12/ARTIljO2qF9aBsuicobXW9pM180112.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。土耳其則以美國牧師[[安德鲁·布伦森|安德鲁·布伦森]]與[[居伦运动|居伦运动]]有牵连為由將其逮捕<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-45854557 |title=土耳其释放美国牧师布伦森 换来特朗普盛赞 |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archive-date=2018-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121015220/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-45854557 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此後美土關係不斷惡化，雙方互相暫停非移民簽證<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-turkey-suspend-non-immigrant-visas-20171009/4062220.html |title=美国土耳其相互暂停非移民签证 |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216113910/https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-turkey-suspend-non-immigrant-visas-20171009/4062220.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，美國一度臨時關閉駐土耳其大使館<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-03/06/c_129823388.htm |title=“安全威胁”致美国驻土耳其大使馆临时关闭 |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216113911/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-03/06/c_129823388.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後又以布伦森被土耳其监禁為由制裁与此案相关的土耳其司法部长和内政部长，同時加倍征收对土耳其的钢铝关税<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-08/15/c_129932898.htm |title=矛盾升级加大土美关系裂痕 |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216113159/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-08/15/c_129932898.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。土耳其轉而向俄羅斯靠攏，並購買[[S-400|S-400]]防空導彈<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/mil/2019-06/25/c_1210169476.htm |title=土外长：土耳其已经买了S400，美国的制裁无法改变这一点 |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216113156/http://www.xinhuanet.com/mil/2019-06/25/c_1210169476.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

